txt.en: 'I will go and hunt for barrow-treasure...just not today.'
'We're the greatest hunters in Bree, and we can't even keep a squirrel out of the lodge.'
'If you have time for a long tale, listen to the stories of Haudh Iarchith from that Ranger.'
'Some of the hunters tried to keep Anglinn out of the lodge...but it doesn't seem to have worked.'
